text: Ab Rosbag (born 14 March 1940) is a Dutch wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman welterweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the Netherlands Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Utrecht (city)
